headline: Aon to Speak at the Goldman Sachs U.S. Financial Services Conference
summary: Edmund Reese, Chief Financial Officer of Aon plc (NYSE: AON), a leading global professional services firm, will speak at the Goldman Sachs U.S. Financial Services Conference in New York on Wednesday, December 10, in a session that begins at 1:00 PM ET.
